---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Finance & Crypto SEO Services - Dominate Financial Search Rankings | Bright Forge SEO" description="Specialized SEO services for financial advisors, fintech companies, cryptocurrency businesses, and investment firms. Drive more qualified leads with expert finance industry SEO.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-chart-line"
    badgeText="Finance & Crypto SEO Experts"
    title="Finance & Crypto SEO Services That Generate High-Value Leads"
    breadcrumbCurrent="Finance & Crypto SEO Services"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>Ready to dominate financial search rankings and attract qualified investors? At Bright Forge <a href="/">SEO Agency</a>, we understand the complex regulatory landscape and unique challenges of finance and cryptocurrency marketing. From financial advisors and fintech startups to crypto exchanges and investment firms, we craft compliant SEO strategies that build trust, drive qualified leads, and establish your authority in the competitive financial sector.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Start Your Finance SEO Strategy" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#services" text="Explore Our Services" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="finance-icon-grid">
          <div class="finance-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
          <div class="finance-icon"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i></div>
          <div class="finance-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
          <div class="finance-icon"><i class="fas fa-university"></i></div>
          <div class="finance-icon"><i class="fas fa-bitcoin"></i></div>
          <div class="finance-icon"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Why Finance SEO Section -->
  <section class="why-finance-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Finance & Crypto Businesses Need <span>Specialized SEO</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="finance-explanation">
        <div class="finance-card">
          <div class="finance-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="finance-text">
            <p>The finance and cryptocurrency industries operate under strict regulatory requirements and face unique trust challenges. Generic SEO strategies fail to address compliance needs, risk management messaging, and the sophisticated decision-making process of financial consumers.</p>
            
            <p>Our finance industry SEO expertise helps you navigate regulatory constraints while building authority and trust. We understand FINRA guidelines, SEC compliance, and cryptocurrency regulations, ensuring your SEO strategy drives qualified leads without compromising compliance or brand reputation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features Section -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Makes Our Finance <span>SEO Services</span> Market-Leading</h2>
        <p>We combine deep financial industry knowledge with proven SEO strategies to drive qualified leads and build trust</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-gavel"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Regulatory Compliance Expertise</h3>
          <p>We understand FINRA, SEC, and cryptocurrency regulations. Our SEO strategies are designed to drive results while maintaining full compliance with financial industry advertising and marketing requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>High-Net-Worth Client Targeting</h3>
          <p>We specialize in attracting qualified, high-value prospects who are actively seeking financial services. Our strategies focus on quality over quantity, driving leads that convert into long-term client relationships.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bitcoin"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Cryptocurrency & DeFi Expertise</h3>
          <p>From crypto exchanges to DeFi platforms, we understand the unique challenges of marketing in the cryptocurrency space. We navigate regulatory uncertainty while building trust in emerging financial technologies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Performance-Based Metrics</h3>
          <p>We track metrics that matter to financial businesses: lead quality, client acquisition cost, assets under management growth, and conversion rates. Our SEO strategies are designed to improve your bottom line.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Trust & Authority Building</h3>
          <p>Financial consumers need to trust you with their money. We create content and SEO strategies that showcase your expertise, credentials, and track record, building the trust that converts prospects into clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ContactSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* Finance Icon Grid (used in Hero visual slot) */
  .hero-image-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .finance-icon-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .finance-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: iconFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .finance-icon:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
  .finance-icon:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .finance-icon:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
  .finance-icon:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .finance-icon:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2s; }
  .finance-icon:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 2.5s; }

  @keyframes iconFloat {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }

  .finance-icon:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1) translateY(-5px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  }

  /* Why Finance Section */
  .why-finance-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .finance-explanation {
    max-width: 4xl;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .finance-card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .finance-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  }

  .finance-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    border-color: #f97316;
  }

  .finance-card .finance-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .finance-card:hover .finance-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.35);
  }

  .finance-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .finance-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #4285F4);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--brand-soft);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    position: relative;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    border: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 5px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.35);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--brand-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .finance-icon-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .finance-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .finance-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    window.toggleFAQ = function(element) {
      const answer = element.nextElementSibling;
      const icon = element.querySelector('i');
      
      if (answer.style.display === 'block') {
        answer.style.display = 'none';
        icon.classList.remove('fa-minus');
        icon.classList.add('fa-plus');
      } else {
        answer.style.display = 'block';
        icon.classList.remove('fa-plus');
        icon.classList.add('fa-minus');
      }
    };
  });
</script>
